 to the graveyard and searched all
night but they could find no one.

"Our son has been stolen by vampires!" the
father cried out to the village people.

Many tried to go into the graveyard, but none
ever returned from there.

The next day, when the father went to the
graveyard, he brought twelve silver bullets with him.
He took his twelve silver bullets and shot the two vampires in their hearts. 


After that, no villager went into the graveyard ever again, for everyone had been warned about the vampires. """
















